self.pm version 0.0.1

self.pm provides 'self' and 'args' methods for your Perl OO modules, so you don't need to
say:

    my $self = shift;

This is no source filter.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

None.


